Name: Pancakes
Recipe: Mix flour, baking powder, and sugar. In a separate bowl, whisk milk and eggs. Combine both mixtures and add melted butter. Cook on a hot griddle until golden brown.

Name: Omelette
Recipe: Beat eggs with milk, salt, and pepper. Melt butter in a pan, pour in the egg mixture, and cook until set. Sprinkle cheese on top and fold the omelette.

Name: Smoothie Bowl
Recipe: Blend banana, berries, and yogurt until smooth. Pour into a bowl and top with granola and a drizzle of honey.

Name: Avocado Toast
Recipe: Toast the bread slices. Mash the avocado with salt, pepper, and lemon juice. Spread the mixture on the toasted bread.

Name: Greek Yogurt with Honey
Recipe: Pour the Greek yogurt into a bowl. Drizzle honey on top and sprinkle with nuts.

Name: Breakfast Burrito
Recipe: Place scrambled eggs, cheese, salsa, and avocado in the center of the tortilla. Roll up the tortilla and serve warm.

Name: Fruit Salad
Recipe: Chop all the fruits and mix in a bowl. Drizzle with honey.

Name: Breakfast Sandwich
Recipe: Fry the egg and assemble the sandwich with bread, cheese, ham, and egg. Grill until golden brown.

Name: Chia Pudding
Recipe: Mix chia seeds and milk. Let it sit overnight in the fridge. Top with honey and berries before serving.

Name: Granola Bars
Recipe: Mix all ingredients and press into a baking dish. Bake at 180°C for 20 minutes. Cut into bars once cooled.

Name: French Toast
Recipe: Whisk egg, milk, cinnamon, and sugar. Dip bread slices in the mixture and fry in butter until golden brown.

Name: Bagel with Cream Cheese
Recipe: Slice the bagel and spread cream cheese on both halves.

Name: Muesli
Recipe: Mix oats, dried fruits, and nuts. Serve with milk and a drizzle of honey.

Name: Scrambled Eggs with Spinach
Recipe: Beat eggs with milk, salt, and pepper. Sauté spinach in butter until wilted. Add eggs and cook until scrambled.

Name: Breakfast Parfait
Recipe: Layer Greek yogurt, granola, and berries in a glass. Drizzle with honey.

Name: Apple Cinnamon Oatmeal
Recipe: Cook oats with milk. Stir in chopped apple, cinnamon, and honey.

Name: Breakfast Quesadilla
Recipe: Scramble eggs and place on one half of the tortilla. Add cheese and salsa, fold the tortilla, and cook in butter until golden brown.

Name: Banana Bread
Recipe: Mash bananas and mix with eggs, melted butter, sugar, and flour. Pour into a loaf pan and bake at 180°C for 60 minutes.

Name: Breakfast Tacos
Recipe: Place scrambled eggs, cheese, salsa, and avocado in tortillas. Serve warm.

Name: Berry Smoothie
Recipe: Blend berries, banana, yogurt, and honey until smooth. Serve chilled.

Name: Peanut Butter Toast
Recipe: Toast bread slices and spread peanut butter on both halves.

Name: Mango Smoothie
Recipe: Blend mango, yogurt, honey, and milk until smooth. Serve chilled.

Name: Breakfast Burrito Bowl
Recipe: Combine scrambled eggs, black beans, cheese, salsa, and avocado in a bowl. Serve warm.

Name: Breakfast Pizza
Recipe: Roll out pizza dough and spread with tomato sauce. Top with scrambled eggs, cheese, and bacon. Bake at 200°C for 15 minutes.

Name: Quinoa Breakfast Bowl
Recipe: Cook quinoa with milk. Stir in honey and top with berries and nuts.

Name: Breakfast Frittata
Recipe: Beat eggs with milk, salt, and pepper. Stir in spinach, tomatoes, and cheese. Pour into a greased baking dish and bake at 180°C for 20 minutes.

Name: Breakfast Wrap
Recipe: Place scrambled eggs, cheese, salsa, and avocado in the center of the tortilla. Roll up the tortilla and serve warm.

Name: Pumpkin Spice Oatmeal
Recipe: Cook oats with milk and pumpkin puree. Stir in cinnamon and honey before serving.

Name: Breakfast Skillet
Recipe: Cook diced potatoes, sausage, onions, and peppers in a skillet until golden brown. Add scrambled eggs and cheese, cook until eggs are set.

Name: Breakfast Muffins
Recipe: Mix flour, sugar, baking powder, and berries. In another bowl, whisk eggs, milk, and melted butter. Combine both mixtures and pour into muffin tins. Bake at 180°C for 20 minutes.

Name: Breakfast Burrito
Recipe: Place scrambled eggs, cheese, salsa, and avocado in the center of the tortilla. Roll up the tortilla and serve warm.

Name: Breakfast Burrito
Recipe: Place scrambled eggs, cheese, salsa, and avocado in the center of the tortilla. Roll up the tortilla and serve warm.

Name: Chicken Caesar Salad
Recipe: Grill chicken breast and slice. Toss romaine lettuce with Caesar dressing. Top with grilled chicken, Parmesan cheese, and croutons.

Name: Turkey Sandwich
Recipe: Layer turkey, lettuce, and tomato between the bread slices. Spread mustard on one slice before assembling.

Name: Veggie Wrap
Recipe: Spread hummus on the tortilla. Layer with sliced vegetables and lettuce. Roll up the tortilla and serve.

Name: Grilled Chicken Sandwich
Recipe: Layer grilled chicken, lettuce, and tomato between the bread slices. Spread mayonnaise on one slice before assembling.

Name: Pasta Salad
Recipe: Cook pasta according to package instructions. Mix with chopped tomatoes, cucumber, feta cheese, olive oil, and lemon juice.

Name: Quinoa Salad
Recipe: Cook quinoa according to package instructions. Mix with chopped bell pepper, cucumber, feta cheese, olive oil, and lemon juice.

Name: Chicken Stir Fry
Recipe: Slice chicken and bell peppers. Sauté garlic and onions in olive oil. Add chicken and cook until done. Stir in bell peppers and soy sauce, cook for another 5 minutes.

Name: Tuna Salad
Recipe: Mix tuna with chopped lettuce, cherry tomatoes, and cucumber. Drizzle with olive oil and lemon juice.

Name: Beef Tacos
Recipe: Cook ground beef until browned. Assemble tacos with beef, lettuce, tomato, cheese, and salsa.

Name: Lentil Soup
Recipe: Sauté chopped carrot, celery, onion, and garlic in olive oil. Add lentils and vegetable broth. Simmer until lentils are tender.

Name: Caprese Salad
Recipe: Slice tomatoes and mozzarella. Arrange on a plate, alternating between the two. Top with fresh basil, drizzle with olive oil and balsamic vinegar.

Name: BBQ Chicken Sandwich
Recipe: Layer BBQ chicken, lettuce, and tomato between the bread slices.

Name: Falafel Wrap
Recipe: Place falafel, lettuce, and tomato in the center of the tortilla. Drizzle with tahini sauce and roll up the tortilla.

Name: Chicken Noodle Soup
Recipe: Sauté chopped carrot, celery, onion, and garlic in olive oil. Add chicken broth and bring to a boil. Add noodles and chicken, cook until noodles are tender and chicken is cooked through.

Name: Veggie Burger
Recipe: Grill veggie patty and place on bun. Top with lettuce, tomato, onion, pickles, ketchup, and mustard.

Name: Chicken Quesadilla
Recipe: Place grilled chicken and cheese on one half of the tortilla. Fold the tortilla and cook in a pan until golden brown. Serve with salsa and sour cream.

Name: Greek Salad
Recipe: Mix chopped tomatoes, cucumber, olives, feta cheese, and red onion. Drizzle with olive oil.

Name: Chicken Pesto Pasta
Recipe: Cook pasta according to package instructions. Toss with grilled chicken and pesto sauce. Top with Parmesan cheese.

Name: Shrimp Tacos
Recipe: Cook shrimp until done. Assemble tacos with shrimp, lettuce, tomato, cheese, and salsa.

Name: Egg Salad Sandwich
Recipe: Chop boiled eggs and mix with mayonnaise and mustard. Spread on bread slices and top with lettuce.

Name: Salmon Salad
Recipe: Grill salmon and flake. Mix with lettuce, cherry tomatoes, and cucumber. Drizzle with olive oil and lemon juice.

Name: Roast Beef Sandwich
Recipe: Layer roast beef, lettuce, and tomato between the bread slices. Spread horseradish sauce on one slice before assembling.

Name: Chicken Cobb Salad
Recipe: Grill chicken breast and slice. Toss lettuce with olive oil. Top with chicken, avocado, bacon, boiled egg, and blue cheese.

Name: Vegetable Soup
Recipe: Sauté chopped carrot, celery, onion, and garlic in olive oil. Add chopped tomatoes and vegetable broth. Simmer until vegetables are tender.

Name: Ham and Cheese Sandwich
Recipe: Layer ham, cheese, lettuce, and tomato between the bread slices. Spread mayonnaise on one slice before assembling.

Name: Chicken and Rice
Recipe: Cook rice according to package instructions. Sauté garlic in olive oil, add chicken and cook until done. Stir in broccoli and soy sauce, cook until broccoli is tender. Serve over rice.

Name: Vegetable Stir Fry
Recipe: Sauté garlic in olive oil, add chopped vegetables and cook until tender. Stir in soy sauce and cook for another 5 minutes.

Name: BLT Sandwich
Recipe: Cook bacon until crispy. Layer bacon, lettuce, and tomato between the bread slices. Spread mayonnaise on one slice before assembling.

Name: Spinach and Feta Wrap
Recipe: Sauté spinach in olive oil until wilted. Place spinach and feta cheese in the center of the tortilla. Roll up the tortilla and serve.

Name: Turkey and Avocado Salad
Recipe: Mix sliced turkey with lettuce, avocado, and cherry tomatoes. Drizzle with olive oil and lemon juice.

Name: Eggplant Parmesan
Recipe: Slice eggplant and bake until tender. Top with tomato sauce, mozzarella, and Parmesan cheese. Bake until cheese is melted. Garnish with basil.

Name: Grilled Salmon
Recipe: Brush salmon fillet with olive oil, minced garlic, and lemon juice. Grill until cooked through. Garnish with chopped parsley.

Name: Beef Stir Fry
Recipe: Sauté beef strips in olive oil until browned. Add chopped bell peppers, broccoli, and garlic. Stir in soy sauce and cook until vegetables are tender.

Name: Chicken Alfredo
Recipe: Cook pasta according to package instructions. Sauté chicken and garlic in olive oil until cooked. Toss with pasta and Alfredo sauce. Top with Parmesan cheese.

Name: Vegetable Curry
Recipe: Sauté chopped onion in oil until soft. Add diced potatoes, carrots, and peas. Stir in curry powder and coconut milk. Simmer until vegetables are tender.

Name: Beef Tacos
Recipe: Cook ground beef until browned. Assemble tacos with beef, lettuce, tomato, cheese, and salsa.

Name: Spaghetti Bolognese
Recipe: Cook spaghetti according to package instructions. Sauté ground beef, onion, and garlic until browned. Stir in tomato sauce and simmer. Serve over spaghetti and top with Parmesan cheese.

Name: Chicken Fajitas
Recipe: Slice chicken, bell peppers, and onion. Sauté in olive oil with fajita seasoning until cooked through. Serve in tortillas.

Name: Shrimp Scampi
Recipe: Cook spaghetti according to package instructions. Sauté shrimp and garlic in olive oil until shrimp is pink. Toss with spaghetti, lemon juice, and chopped parsley.

Name: Beef Stew
Recipe: Sauté beef chunks until browned. Add chopped potatoes, carrots, onion, and garlic. Pour in beef broth and simmer until vegetables are tender.

Name: Vegetable Lasagna
Recipe: Layer lasagna noodles, tomato sauce, spinach, ricotta, and mozzarella in a baking dish. Repeat layers. Top with Parmesan cheese. Bake until bubbly and golden.

Name: Chicken Parmesan
Recipe: Bread chicken breast with breadcrumbs and fry in olive oil until golden. Top with tomato sauce and mozzarella. Bake until cheese is melted. Sprinkle with Parmesan.

Name: Lamb Chops
Recipe: Marinate lamb chops in olive oil, garlic, and rosemary. Grill until desired doneness. Serve with roasted potatoes and green beans.

Name: Chicken Tikka Masala
Recipe: Cook chicken in tikka masala sauce until done. Serve over cooked rice. Garnish with yogurt and chopped cilantro.

Name: Vegetable Stir Fry
Recipe: Sauté garlic in olive oil, add chopped vegetables and cook until tender. Stir in soy sauce and cook for another 5 minutes.

Name: Pork Chops
Recipe: Sear pork chops in olive oil until browned. Remove from pan and add sliced apples and onion. Cook until soft. Return pork chops to pan and sprinkle with thyme. Serve with mashed potatoes.

Name: Quinoa Salad
Recipe: Cook quinoa according to package instructions. Mix with chopped cucumber, cherry tomatoes, and feta cheese. Drizzle with olive oil and lemon juice.

Name: Seafood Paella
Recipe: Sauté bell peppers in olive oil. Add rice and saffron, stir until rice is coated. Add broth and bring to a simmer. Add shrimp, mussels, and peas. Cook until seafood is done and rice is tender.

Name: Stuffed Peppers
Recipe: Cut tops off bell peppers and remove seeds. Sauté ground beef and onion until browned. Mix with cooked rice and tomato sauce. Stuff mixture into bell peppers. Top with cheese and bake until peppers are tender.

Name: Chicken Caesar Salad
Recipe: Grill chicken breast and slice. Toss lettuce with Caesar dressing. Top with chicken, Parmesan cheese, and croutons.

Name: Vegetarian Chili
Recipe: Sauté onion, bell peppers, and garlic in oil until soft. Add kidney beans, chopped tomatoes, and chili powder. Simmer until thickened.

Name: BBQ Ribs
Recipe: Marinate pork ribs in BBQ sauce, minced garlic, chopped onion, and brown sugar. Bake in the oven or grill until tender.

Name: Fish and Chips
Recipe: Coat fish fillets in a batter made from flour and beer. Fry until golden. Serve with fries made from sliced potatoes. Accompany with tartar sauce.

Name: Mushroom Risotto
Recipe: Sauté chopped onion and mushrooms in olive oil until soft. Add Arborio rice and cook for 1 minute. Gradually add vegetable broth, stirring constantly, until rice is creamy and tender. Top with Parmesan cheese.

Name: Beef Stroganoff
Recipe: Sauté beef strips in butter until browned. Remove from pan and add chopped mushrooms and onion. Cook until soft. Stir in beef broth and simmer. Return beef to pan and stir in sour cream. Serve over noodles or rice.

Name: Chicken Fried Rice
Recipe: Cook rice according to package instructions. Sauté chopped chicken, peas, and carrot in oil until cooked. Add cooked rice, soy sauce, and garlic. Stir in beaten egg and cook until set.

Name: Vegetable Casserole
Recipe: Layer sliced potatoes, carrots, and green beans in a baking dish. Top with chopped onion and cheese. Pour cream over the top. Bake until vegetables are tender and cheese is melted and bubbly.

Name: Turkey Meatloaf
Recipe: Mix ground turkey with breadcrumbs, egg, chopped onion, garlic, and tomato sauce. Shape into a loaf and bake until cooked through.

Name: Vegetarian Pizza
Recipe: Spread tomato sauce over pizza dough. Top with mozzarella cheese, sliced bell peppers, mushrooms, and onion. Bake until crust is golden and cheese is melted.

Name: Steak and Potatoes
Recipe: Season steak with salt and pepper and grill to desired doneness. Serve with roasted potatoes tossed in melted butter, garlic, and rosemary.

Name: Chicken Enchiladas
Recipe: Cook and shred chicken breast. Mix with chopped onion and cheese. Roll mixture into tortillas and place in a baking dish. Pour enchilada sauce over the top and bake until bubbly.

Name: Grilled Vegetables
Recipe: Slice zucchini, bell peppers, and eggplant. Toss with olive oil and minced garlic. Grill until tender. Garnish with chopped basil.

Name: Pasta Primavera
Recipe: Cook pasta according to package instructions. Sauté cherry tomatoes, broccoli, and bell peppers in olive oil with minced garlic. Toss with cooked pasta.

Name: Shrimp Tacos
Recipe: Cook shrimp in a skillet until pink. Assemble tacos with shrimp, shredded cabbage, sliced avocado, and salsa. Serve with lime wedges.
